<view class="container">
  <view class="user-card">
    <image class="avatar" src="{{userInfo.avatarUrl}}" mode="aspectFill" />
    <text class="nickname">{{userInfo.nickName || '点击头像登录'}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="menu-list">
    <navigator url="/pages/profile/profile" class="menu-item">
      <text>宝宝信息</text>
      <text class="tip-text">过敏食材、BLW喜欢/不喜欢</text>
      <text class="arrow">›</text>
    </navigator>
    <navigator url="/pages/recipes/recipes" class="menu-item">
      <text>我的菜谱</text>
      <text class="tip-text">管理常用菜谱</text>
      <text class="arrow">›</text>
    </navigator>
    <navigator url="/pages/logs/logs" class="menu-item">
      <text>进食记录</text>
      <text class="tip-text">按天倒序、异常标记</text>
      <text class="arrow">›</text>
    </navigator>
  </view>

  <view class="footer-tip tip-text">
    ✔️ 已帮你保存偏好，生成计划时会自动排除过敏食材哦
  </view>
</view>
